                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900915-18-defend217 t17900915-18-punish93"></join>
               Fined one shilling
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17900915-18-punish94" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900915-18-punish94" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-18-punish94" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="newgate"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900915-18-defend217 t17900915-18-punish94"></join>
               imprisoned one month in Newgate
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
